Belief-Changer licensing
========================

Software
--------

Unless a file says otherwise, software authored for this repository is
licensed under the GNU Affero General Public License, version 3 or any later
version (`AGPL-3.0-or-later`). This includes executable source code, scripts,
and software configuration.

Official license text:
https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.html

Project-owned content
---------------------

Unless a file says otherwise, original non-software material authored for this
repository is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0
International license (`CC-BY-SA-4.0`). This includes project-owned books,
prompts, templates, documentation, research metadata, and research synthesis.

Official legal code:
https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/legalcode.en

Third-party material and personal data
--------------------------------------

These grants apply only to material the project owns or is authorized to
license. They do not relicense third-party works, quotations, excerpts, source
captures, trademarks, publicity or privacy rights, or personal data.

In particular, files under `analysis/reference-books/`, third-party source
files under `production-books/*/research/sources/`, and attributed third-party
passages retain their original rights and terms unless an adjacent notice says
otherwise. Their presence in the repository is not a license grant from this
project. Contributors must record the source, attribution, license or other
rights basis, and any changes for third-party material they add.

Where a file mixes project-owned and third-party material, the applicable
project license covers only the project-owned contribution. No rights are
granted beyond those the project controls.
